<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٢٢:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَآيَةٌ لَهُمْ أَنَّا حَمَلْنَا ذُرِّيَّتَهُمْ فِي الْفُلْكِ الْمَشْحُونِ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span> وَخَلَقْنَا لَهُمْ مِنْ مِثْلِهِ مَا يَرْكَبُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[يس: ٤١، ٤٢]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَيُذْكَرُ عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ:</span> <span class="c3">{المَشْحُونِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«المُوقَرُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ مِثْلِهِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مِنَ الأَنْعَامِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>